@startuml
title Hybrid Dependencies Analysis - Main Flow

actor User

boundary Auth as "Authentication"
boundary Project as "Project Manager"
boundary Parser as "Parse Engine"
boundary Analyzer as "Analysis Engine"
boundary Report as "Report Service"
database DB as "Database"
collections FS as "File System"

== 1. Register / Login ==

User -> Auth: POST /user/register
Auth -> DB: save user
DB --> Auth: OK
Auth --> User: Result.success()

User -> Auth: GET /user/login
Auth -> DB: verify user
DB --> Auth: UserDAO
Auth --> User: JWT Token

== 2. Upload Project ==

User -> Project: POST /sourceFolder/upload (ZIP)
Project -> Project: unzip archive
Project -> DB: save folder info
DB --> Project: sourceFolderId
Project --> User: Result.success(sourceFolderId)

== 3. Source Parsing ==

User -> Parser: POST /parse/parseAll?sourceFolderId=1
Parser -> FS: walk project directory

group Java Parsing
  Parser -> Parser: Spoon parse .java files
  Parser -> Parser: extract classes, fields, methods, annotations, imports
  Parser -> FS: write java-parse-output.json
  Parser -> DB: save parse record
end

group JSP Parsing
  Parser -> Parser: Jasper/Regex parse .jsp files
  Parser -> FS: write jsp-parse-output.json
  Parser -> DB: save parse record
end

group JSF Parsing
  Parser -> Parser: Jsoup parse .xhtml files
  Parser -> FS: write jsf-parse-output.json
  Parser -> DB: save parse record
end

group XML Parsing
  Parser -> Parser: parse web.xml / persistence.xml / ejb-jar.xml / faces-config.xml / pom.xml
  Parser -> FS: write each XML parse output JSON
  Parser -> DB: save parse records
end

Parser --> User: Result.success()

== 4. Static Analysis ==

User -> Analyzer: POST /StaticAnalysis/annotationAnalysis
Analyzer -> FS: read java-parse-output.json
Analyzer -> Analyzer: count annotation usage
Analyzer -> Analyzer: generate migration suggestions
Analyzer -> FS: write annotation-statistics.json
Analyzer -> DB: save analysis result (insertResult / updateResult)
DB --> Analyzer: OK
Analyzer --> User: Result.success(report)
note right
  Other analyses:
  WebXml / FileStore / Persistence
  / EJB / POM / FacesConfig
end note

== 5. View Reports ==

User -> Report: GET /reports/AnnotationReport
Report -> DB: query analysis path (getAnnotationReport)
DB --> Report: AnalysisReportDAO (includes path)
Report -> FS: read report JSON file
FS --> Report: report content
Report --> User: Result.success(reportData)
note right
  Other reports:
  WebXmlReport / FileStoreReport
  / PersistenceReport / EjbJarReport
  / PomXmlReport / FacesConfigReport
end note

@enduml
